channel.title: Sorry just need help with the status page
channel.description: Well I have made a new ip for my server, and I don't know how to change it. It keeps saying my server is offline and it is not. Does anyone know how I can change my ip so it says my server is online? It has 440+ votes and it would be a shame if I could not do anything to change this old ip.
